data.description: Experience the best of country living with this stunning 20 acre property! A true hobby farm, ideal for cattle or horses, complete with a chicken coop and a spacious hay barn, ready to accommodate your equipment and storage needs. The land has been thoughtfully fenced and cross-fenced, featuring waterers in each section. You'll find both a hay field and grazing pasture, along with a working pen to streamline your farming activities. The gates and posts have been freshly painted, and the new fencing enhances the aesthetics. With Hwy 60 frontage, this property not only offers a haven for your animals, but also showcases its rural charm to passersby. The 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers ample space and comfort. As you step inside the house, you'll find a convenient mudroom and breezeway connecting your indoor and outdoor living spaces with ease. Relax in the sun-room, offering a peaceful retreat, along with a finished basement that could be transformed into a gym or additional living space. To welcome you home, a long concrete driveway is gracefully lined with Bradford pear trees, creating a stunning entrance to your countryside sanctuary. Embrace the rural lifestyle you've always dreamed of on this extraordinary hobby farm. Don't miss out on this unique property that combines rural charm and modern comfort!
